# Scanner-generated research / prefilter output (2,292+ .md files)
# Gitignored 2026-04-17: these dirs churn constantly from background scans
# and dominated the working tree. Files stay on disk; only git stops tracking.
# Template files like _queue.txt remain tracked; only .md output is ignored.
# Research notes that need to be shared should live elsewhere (e.g., docs/).
data/company-intel/*.md
!data/company-intel/.gitkeep
data/prefilter-results/*.md
!data/prefilter-results/.gitkeep

# Brain staging output (regenerated from applications.md + responses.md by migrations)
data/brain-stats-cache.json
data/brain-staging-applications/
data/brain-staging-intel/
data/brain-staging-people/
data/brain-staging-reports/

# Application dispatch records (operational state, contains form-fill data + local paths)
data/apply-runs/

# Cron single-instance lock files (data/.locks/<task>.lock)
data/.locks/

# Build artifacts (regenerable)
data/index/
data/run-summaries/
dashboard.html
review.html

# Per-source scanner health (runtime state, regenerated each scan)
data/source-health.json

# package-from-report.mjs outputs (per-app deliverables; same rationale as output/)
packages/*
!packages/.gitkeep

